oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Discussion Paper Series in Economics and Business Statistics
Collection
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Akimov, Alexandr
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The Discussion Paper Series in Economics and Business Statistics represents work in progress from the Department Accounting, Finance and Economics on a range of issues in economics and business statistics. The papers are also published to the Research Papers in Economics (RePEc) web database of working papers, journals articles and software components.
